Описание:
Greetings from our friendly and successful WGG Advertising Agency team!
WGG is looking for a specialist in the field of Meta & TikTok advertising.
Friendly relations, a comfortable environment, achieving results at work and continuous development of employees are our core values. We are really good at helping businesses grow, for example, by increasing turnover 20 times in a year. Our clients include both medium and small businesses, as well as such giants as SAP, Fam Properties and others.
We are always glad to see talented people in our team who want to build an international career!
Let's start with what we'll do for you:
We’ll add large, complex and interesting projects to your portfolio;
We will give you the opportunity to develop professionally, experienced mentors will prompt you and will be there for you;
We will give you the opportunity to work with all existing niches - from personal brands to large manufacturing companies.
What will you do:
Execute media buying strategies on platforms like Facebook, TikTok;
Monitor campaign performance, identify trends, and refine strategies for maximum impact;
Work with the marketing and creative teams to align campaigns with brand messaging;
Create advertising creatives independently and set technical tasks for the Design team to develop visual materials;
Provide detailed performance insights to stakeholders and recommend improvements.
What we offer:
Competitive salary;
Interesting international projects;
The opportunity to grow quickly;
Working five days a week, from 10:00 to 19:00 Dubai time;
Convenient remote working format.

